641
00:27:06,667 --> 00:27:08,751
On behalf
of the Attorney General,

642
00:27:08,834 --> 00:27:10,459
the Joint Chiefs of Staff,

643
00:27:10,542 --> 00:27:12,417
the members
of the Supreme Court,

644
00:27:12,500 --> 00:27:15,876
