00:28:51,876 --> 00:28:53,459
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

666
00:28:53,542 --> 00:28:56,584
GEORGE:<i> I said, "I've got to</i>
<i>take a stand in New York.</i>"

667
00:28:56,667 --> 00:28:59,751
<i>I've got to do television here.
