and I've noticed something
about them.

694
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:04,542
When the Westerns
involve Indians,

695
00:30:04,626 --> 00:30:06,709
and sometimes they don't,
sometimes it's Brian Donlevy

696
00:30:06,792 --> 00:30:08,375
