702
00:30:22,083 --> 00:30:24,250
(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

703
00:30:24,334 --> 00:30:26,959
"All right, all the tall guys
over by the trees."

704
00:30:27,042 --> 00:30:33,125
(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

705
00:30:33,209 --> 00:30:35,042
"Fat guys
down behind the rocks."

706
00:30:35,125 --> 00:30:39,042
(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

707
00:30:39,125 --> 00:30:41,125
"You with the beads,
