708
00:30:41,209 --> 00:30:45,417
(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

709
00:30:46,584 --> 00:30:48,250
"All right,
knock off the horseplay."

710
00:30:48,334 --> 00:30:49,918
Come on,
knock off the horseplay.

711
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,626
Come on, you guys over there
playing with the horse,

712
00:30:51,709 --> 00:30:55,334
-will you knock it off?"
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING, APPLAUDING)

713
00:30:55,417 --> 00:30:57,334
GEORGE:<i> There'll be a rain dance</i>
<i>Friday night.</i>

714
00:30:57,417 --> 00:31:01,876
<i>-Weather permitting.</i>
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

715
00:31:01,959 --> 00:31:03,626
GEORGE:<i> I got my Merv Griffin</i>
<i>and they gave me</i>

716
00:31:03,709 --> 00:31:04,584
<i>three more shots.</i>

717
00:31:04,667 --> 00:31:05,876
ANNOUNCER:
<i>Here is George Carlin.</i>

718
00:31:05,959 --> 00:31:07,125
GEORGE:<i> I had been working</i>
<i>for a year-and-a-half</i>

719
00:31:07,209 --> 00:31:08,584
<i>just to get
five minutes together,</i>

720
00:31:08,667 --> 00:31:10,834
<i>and suddenly
there were these three dates</i>

721
00:31:10,918 --> 00:31:12,334
<i>staring at me within a month.</i>

722
00:31:12,417 --> 00:31:13,417
<i>Thank you very much.</i>

