00:34:22,042 --> 00:34:24,667
He's really breaking up,
just the way accountants laugh.

805
00:34:24,751 --> 00:34:25,792
They like to keep it neat.

806
00:34:25,876 --> 00:34:27,417
-(LAUGHS RESTRAINEDLY)
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

