00:34:27,500 --> 00:34:29,709
I once worked a whole
convention of accountants.

808
00:34:29,792 --> 00:34:31,751
-(LAUGHS FAINTLY)
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

809
00:34:31,834 --> 00:34:32,834
Kind of strange.

810
00:34:32,918 --> 00:34:33,959
Richard, what's your
favorite kind of laughter?

811
00:34:34,042 --> 00:34:35,250
Well, I got a laugh.
I don't know

812
00:34:35,334 --> 00:34:36,584
if it's my favorite,
but it's one I hear

