00:34:36,667 --> 00:34:39,000
above everyone else's,
sort of a witch's laugh

814
00:34:39,083 --> 00:34:42,626
-(CACKLES)
-(AUDIENCE LAUGHING)

815
00:34:42,709 --> 00:34:47,834
-Kind of scares you... (CACKLES)
